# Ignore common test and development files in security scans
**/tests/*
**/vendor/*
**/node_modules/*
**/.git/*
**/.env*
**/storage/logs/*
**/storage/framework/*

# Ignore common build artifacts
**/build/*
**/dist/*
**/public/build/*
**/public/storage/*

# But scan these security-critical files
!**/composer.json
!**/composer.lock
!**/package.json
!**/package-lock.json
!**/yarn.lock
!**/config/**/*
!**/routes/**/*
!**/app/Http/Middleware/**/*
!**/app/Providers/**/*
